{"word":"G2440 - ἱμάτιον - himátion - him-at'-ee-on - Apparel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱμάτιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>himátion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>him-at'-ee-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Apparel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வஸ்திரம், அங்கி - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a garment"},{"paragraph":"2. the upper garment, the cloak or mantle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Neuter of a presumed derivative of <b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03BD;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>hennumi</b> (to <i>put on</i>); a <i>dress</i> (inner or outer): - apparel, cloke, clothes, garment, raiment, robe, vesture."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2439 - ἱματίζω - himatízō - him-at-id'-zo/2439\">G2439</a>, <a href=\"#/G2440 - ἱμάτιον - himátion - him-at'-ee-on/2440\">G2440</a>, <a href=\"#/G2441 - ἱματισμός - himatismós - him-at-is-mos'/2441\">G2441</a>"}]}